				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Kh%E1%BA%AFc/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-di%E1%BB%87p-ho%C3%A0ng-Th%E1%BB%A5-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-s%C6%A1-nh%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%99t-c%C6%B0u-minh/poem-Eah8blL_w_uJxKxx_IsGlQ">Đậu diệp hoàng (Thụ đầu sơ nhật bột cưu minh) - 豆葉黃（樹頭初日鵓鳩鳴）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Kh%E1%BA%AFc/author-E0HetHpe9CvZ-elxTRGRbw">Trần Khắc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/Ho%E1%BA%A1-T%E1%BA%A5n-L%C4%83ng-L%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BB%ABa-T%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n-du-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-r1yBbvknGqsl7_MlyowiqQ">Hoạ Tấn Lăng Lục thừa “Tảo xuân du vọng” - 和晉陵陸丞早春遊望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/author-m8VtavBW4Ya78m3-y_Q_Gw">Đỗ Thẩm Ngôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/Nam-du/poem-bSWNOGFPupghOcCR87O78w">Nam du - 南遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%E1%BB%91c/author-dSnmLveHQYvLVD8-n4k18A">Trịnh Cốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-D%E1%BA%ADt-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng/Nam-ph%E1%BB%91-L%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i/poem-zjirqPOe4YlREUrvB9qD3w">Nam phố - Lữ hoài - 南浦－旅懹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-D%E1%BA%ADt-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng/author-gBi6of_5SqKChP9lnhM8WA">Lỗ Dật Trọng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Ninh-Minh-giang-k%C3%BD-ki%E1%BA%BFn/poem-BhGwNsQxXC1PDoPFqJY9GA">Ninh Minh giang ký kiến - 寧明江記見</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/S%C6%A1-xu%C3%A2n/poem-bU22Zz9-NAHRz3R5RedMkA">Sơ xuân - 初春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A0nh/author-HYGFT6wTz4aNfPlamWDBRw">Nguyễn Tử Thành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-T%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3/Th%E1%BB%A9-H%E1%BB%93ng-T%C3%A0o-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qdmRxZdpHgoFjpdE1ZQs3w">Thứ Hồng Tào vận - 次洪漕韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-T%C6%B0-Qu%E1%BB%B3/author-vKbY4mxW66T2uFN2-wgrVw">Hồng Tư Quỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-c%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-6krcYPpWfsYF0wFw7ZDeSA">Thưởng cúc kỳ 07 - 賞菊其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ti%E1%BB%83u-h%C3%A0n/poem-wF1IhcmSqNBXfkUJaKIi2w">Tiểu hàn - 小寒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/V%C4%83n-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-FnnTxBaON8h_Pp60oZXQBg">Văn địch - 聞笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
